board.name: FM192-RU
board.description: FM192 is an FMC board compatible with EMC2-DP to provide Wireless communication (4G, WiFi, BLE, GPS), apart from 3VTTL I/Os, ADC (12 channels), DAC (8 channels) and USB 3.0 (2xUSB-C + 1xUSB-C-IP67 + 1xUSB-A ports), targeting robotics applications.

component.name: onboardleds
component.description: LEDs available at the FM192. They will light up when high active

component.name: onboardgpios
component.description: GPIOs available at the FM192, accessible at the 40pin GPIO header.

component.name: i2c_fmcbus
component.description: I2C bus on the FMC module

component.name: adc_uart
component.description: 3 UARTs to communicate with the ADCs.

component.name: adc_uart_rq
component.description: RQ pins of the ADCs on FM192.

component.name: hl7800_uart
component.description: 2 x UARTs to communicate with HL7800

component.name: hl7800_uart_rts
component.description: RTS pins of the HL7800 on FM192.

component.name: hl7800_uart_cts
component.description: CTS pins of the HL7800 on FM192.

component.name: bx3100_uart_rts
component.description: RTS pins of the BX3100 on FM192.

component.name: bx3100_uart_cts
component.description: CTS pins of the BX3100 on FM192.

component.name: control_signals
component.description: [0..4]: TX_ON, RESET_IN, WAKE_UP, FAST_SHUTDOWN (HL7800) and ENABLE (BX3100).
